data.description: Welcome to 5686 Newberry Point Dr, Flowery Branch, GA, where modern comfort meets luxury. Just a couple of miles from Lake Lanier!!! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, complete with a partially finished basement, sits on a generous 1.3-acre lot in the Newberry Point neighborhood. Offering a total of 2,465 square feet on the main level and an additional 2,465 square feet in the basement, there's ample space for your family to flourish.    Upon entering, you'll immediately sense the welcoming atmosphere of this meticulously maintained residence. The semi open-concept floor plan seamlessly combines the living, dining, and kitchen areas, drenched in natural light from large windows.  The main level also features three spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms, including a master suite with an en-suite bathroom, perfect for unwinding.    Descend to the basement and discover a hidden gem—currently a theater/media room with a JVC projector, a movie screen that's 9 x 10', a media cabinet that contains a Yamaha receiver six speakers a media streamer for terabyte hard drive with 2000 movie files 100 concert videos 300 cartoons and 7500 music files, a full bathroom, office space, and an extra bedroom. This lower level offers endless possibilities for customization.     The beautiful screen den porch comes complete with plastic panels, making winter icing easy and year-round use of the screen den porch.     Outside, the sprawling 1.3-acre lot is meticulously landscaped, providing the perfect backdrop for outdoor activities. A spacious deck, fire pit, and patio invite relaxation and entertainment.    Additional features include a two-car garage, convenient access to shopping and dining, top-rated schools, and impeccable curb appeal.    This exceptional property at 5686 Newberry Point Dr is more than a home; it's an invitation to embrace the finest of Georgia living. Don't miss your opportunity to make this your forever home. Contact us today for a private showing and start living your dream in Flowery Branch!
